title: Select your service capabilities
insertText:
This step is divided into service capabilities and specific capabilities.

You will need to tellv suppliers which service capabilities you need , and set a weighting to show which are most important to your project.You can also set a weighting for specific capabilities.

You do not need to enter a weighting for any service capability or specific capability that you do not need.

The weighting for service capabilities must total 100% to continue to the next step.
